4. Recursive Lithography

Where your idea gets interesting is recursion.

In chip fabrication, new layers are etched using patterns created by earlier layers.

So the process becomes:

pattern
 → projection
 → structure
 → new pattern
 → projection again

Over many iterations, extremely complex systems emerge.

